      },
      "description": [
        "{{sbc|Innate:}} Upon taking {{tip|death|fatal damage}}, '''Karthus''' enters a '''{{tip|zombie state}}''' for 7 seconds, during which he can cast his abilities at no cost. If ''{{ai|Defile|Karthus}}'' has been learned, it will remain toggled on for ''Death Defied's'' entire duration. ''{{ai|Requiem|Karthus}}'' becomes disabled after ''Death Defied'' has lasted 4 seconds.",
        "While under this state, '''Karthus''' becomes {{tip|untargetable}} and {{tip|cc-immune|immune to crowd control}} as well as prevents all incoming damage, but is also rendered unable to move, declare [[basic attack]]s, use [[summoner spell]]s, and [[Active ability items|activate items]]."
      ],
      "descriptionHtml": "<span class=\"sbc\">Innate:</span> Upon taking <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">fatal damage<template #content><div><h4>death<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword death</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>, <b>Karthus</b> enters a <b><HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">zombie state<template #content><div><h4>zombie state<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword zombie state</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip></b> for 7 seconds, during which he can cast his abilities at no cost. If <i><span class=\"ai\">Karthus's Defile</span></i> has been learned, it will remain toggled on for <i>Death Defied's</i> entire duration. <i><span class=\"ai\">Karthus's Requiem</span></i> becomes disabled after <i>Death Defied</i> has lasted 4 seconds.<br />While under this state, <b>Karthus</b> becomes <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">untargetable<template #content><div><h4>untargetable<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword untargetable</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip> and <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">immune to crowd control<template #content><div><h4>cc-immune<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword cc-immune</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip> as well as prevents all incoming damage, but is also rendered unable to move, declare <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"basic attack\">basic attack</a>s, use <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"summoner spell\">summoner spell</a>s, and <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"activate items\">Active ability items</a>.",
      "leveling": [],
      "notes": "* ''Death Defied's'' {{tip|untargetability}} does not {{tip|homing projectile destruction|destroy}} in-flight {{tip|projectiles}}.\n* '''Karthus''' cannot be {{tip|execute|executed}} by the {{bi|Aspect of the Dragon}} during ''Death Defied''.\n* At the start of ''Death Defied'', '''Karthus''' is set to {{sti|health|{{as|1 health}}}}.\n** '''Karthus''' can still regenerate his health over the duration, but he will always die at the end of it.\n* After ''Death Defied'' ends, the corpse of '''Karthus''' will retain [[unit collision]] despite being dead on the ground.\n* '''Karthus' ''' [[health bar|mana bar]] drains over the duration of ''Death Defied'' as an indicator of his time remaining in this state.\n{{Zombie state info}}",
      "skillletter": "I",
      "skillkey": "I",
      "skillid": 1,
      "skillwiki": "I",
      "effects": []
    },
